Items.Title: Resolution calling upon the New York State Legislature to adopt and the Governor to sign legislation which would allow credit unions, savings banks, and savings and loan associations to accept and secure deposits from municipal corporations.
Items.ActionText: This Resolution was Hearing Held by Committee
Items.MatterName: Allow credit unions, savings banks, savings and loan associations to accept and secure deposits from municipal corporations.
